name: TriipMiles
public_notice: TIIM has migrated from TOMOCHAIN to Binance Smart Chain - https://bscscan.com/token/0x3da4f9e86deef7c50a8b167493f26e894edcd7d5. For more information, visit https://twitter.com/triipme/status/1444857333436219394?s=21

description.en: Triip is a blockchain-enabled travel platform allows for direct interactions between service providers and clients. Using a propriety token, Triip Miles or TIIM,  Triip  is a network that enables greater transparency, security and lower cost transactions between those who travel and those who serve them.
